---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="EmpowerNow – Identity & Authorization Fabric" description="AI-native identity orchestration and AuthZEN-compliant authorization platform" canonical="/">
	<section class="container" style="padding:200px 0 80px">
		<div style="display:flex;gap:64px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap">
			<div style="flex:1 1 420px;min-width:320px;max-width:560px">
				<div style="display:inline-block;padding:8px 24px;border:1px solid var(--border-strong);border-radius:999px;color:var(--on-surface);background:var(--surface-2);font-weight:600;margin-bottom:32px">Designed for AI, by AI</div>
				<h1 class="display" style="font-size:60px;line-height:1.1;margin:0 0 12px">Secure every human, service, and AI agent with one <span style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--color-accent),var(--color-primary));-webkit-background-clip:text;background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent">Identity & Authorization Fabric</span></h1>
				<p style="color:#9ba3b7;max-width:720px;margin:0 0 20px">AuthZEN evaluation with constraints and obligations. OAuth Token Exchange, RAR, optional DPoP. MCP‑aware enforcement and cryptographic receipts.</p>
				<ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin:18px 0 28px;max-width:640px;color:#9ba3b7">
					<li style="display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:8px"><span style="color:var(--color-accent)">•</span> One fabric for people, services, and AI agents</li>
					<li style="display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:8px"><span style="color:var(--color-accent)">•</span> Policy‑gated AI workflows with spend limits</li>
					<li style="display:flex;gap:8px"><span style="color:var(--color-accent)">•</span> Tamper‑evident receipts and full observability</li>
				</ul>
				<div style="display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap">
					<a class="btn btn-primary" href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}resources/demo/`}>Watch the 10‑min Demo</a>
					<a class="btn" href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}products/`}>Explore Products</a>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div style="flex:1 1 420px;min-width:320px;max-width:520px">
				<img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/login-background.jpg`} alt="Platform preview" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:16px;box-shadow:0 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.4)" />
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="container" style="padding:40px 0">
		<div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:32px">
			<h2 style="font-size:40px;margin:0 0 8px">Plug • Protect • Propel</h2>
			<p style="color:#9ba3b7">Outcome‑focused capabilities delivered by EmpowerNow.</p>
		</div>
		<div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(260px,1fr));gap:24px">
			<div class="glass-card" style="padding:28px;text-align:center">
				<h3 style="margin:0 0 8px">Plug</h3>
				<p style="color:#9ba3b7">Zero‑code connectors light up any system in minutes.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="glass-card" style="padding:28px;text-align:center">
				<h3 style="margin:0 0 8px">Protect</h3>
				<p style="color:#9ba3b7">Graph‑anchored policies redact and revoke in real time.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="glass-card" style="padding:28px;text-align:center">
				<h3 style="margin:0 0 8px">Propel</h3>
				<p style="color:#9ba3b7">AI agents execute workflows safely at machine speed.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="container" style="padding:60px 0">
		<div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:40px">
			<h2 style="font-size:40px;margin:0 0 8px">Our Products</h2>
			<p style="color:#9ba3b7">Enterprise‑grade identity orchestration and authorization infrastructure.</p>
		</div>
		<div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(280px,1fr));gap:24px">
			<a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}products/pdp/`} class="glass-card" style="padding:28px;text-decoration:none;color:inherit">
				<div style="font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#9ba3b7;margin-bottom:8px">Lead Engine</div>
				<h3 style="margin:0 0 8px">Authorization Studio</h3>
				<p style="color:var(--color-accent);margin:0 0 8px">OpenID AuthZEN PDP</p>
				<p style="color:#9ba3b7">Industry‑standard policy decision point with delegation graphs, batch evaluation, and explainable decisions.</p>
			</a>
			<a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}products/orchestration/`} class="glass-card" style="padding:28px;text-decoration:none;color:inherit">
				<div style="font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#9ba3b7;margin-bottom:8px">Lead Engine</div>
				<h3 style="margin:0 0 8px">Automation Studio</h3>
				<p style="color:var(--color-accent);margin:0 0 8px">AI‑Powered Orchestrator</p>
				<p style="color:#9ba3b7">Drag, drop, deploy AI workflows—identity‑secured and policy‑gated.</p>
			</a>
			<a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}products/idp/`} class="glass-card" style="padding:28px;text-decoration:none;color:inherit">
				<h3 style="margin:0 0 8px">Authentication Studio</h3>
				<p style="color:var(--color-accent);margin:0 0 8px">FAPI 2.0‑Ready IdP</p>
				<p style="color:#9ba3b7">Passkeys, OIDC, adaptive risk; issue FAPI‑profiled tokens and fine‑grained on‑behalf‑of credentials for agents.</p>
			</a>
			<a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}products/registry/`} class="glass-card" style="padding:28px;text-decoration:none;color:inherit">
				<h3 style="margin:0 0 8px">Inventory Studio</h3>
				<p style="color:var(--color-accent);margin:0 0 8px">Universal Collector</p>
				<p style="color:#9ba3b7">Discover, diff, and reconcile identities at scale with policy‑gated writes.</p>
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="container" style="padding:40px 0">
		<h2 style="font-size:32px;margin:0 0 12px">Standards & Interop</h2>
		<ul style="color:#9ba3b7;line-height:1.8;margin:0">
			<li>OpenID Authorization API (AuthZEN) — evaluation endpoints</li>
			<li>OAuth Token Exchange (RFC 8693), RAR (RFC 9396), DPoP (RFC 9449)</li>
			<li>Model Context Protocol (MCP) for agent‑tool calls</li>
			<li>Signed, hash‑chained receipts for auditability</li>
		</ul>
	</section>

	<section class="container" style="padding:60px 0">
		<div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:40px">
			<h2 style="font-size:40px;margin:0 0 8px">Why EmpowerNow?</h2>
			<p style="color:#9ba3b7">Modern identity and authorization infrastructure for AI‑era workloads.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="grid-3" style="gap:24px">
			<div class="glass-card" style="padding:28px;text-align:center">
				<h3 style="margin:0 0 8px">AI‑Native Design</h3>
				<p style="color:#9ba3b7">Built for people, services, and AI agents as first‑class identities.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="glass-card" style="padding:28px;text-align:center">
				<h3 style="margin:0 0 8px">Zero Trust Ready</h3>
				<p style="color:#9ba3b7">Continuous verification and dynamic, explainable policies.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="glass-card" style="padding:28px;text-align:center">
				<h3 style="margin:0 0 8px">Full Observability</h3>
				<p style="color:#9ba3b7">Every decision explained; complete, tamper‑evident audit trails.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="container" style="padding:80px 0 120px;text-align:center">
		<h2 style="font-size:40px;margin:0 0 12px">Ready to get started?</h2>
		<p style="color:#9ba3b7;max-width:720px;margin:0 auto 20px">Join teams using EmpowerNow for identity orchestration and AuthZEN‑compliant authorization.</p>
		<div style="display:flex;gap:12px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap">
			<a class="btn btn-primary" href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}resources/demo/`}>Watch the 10‑min Demo</a>
			<a class="btn" href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}demo/`}>Book a Demo</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</Base>
